;Cutting Out the Junk
Slip af med skidtet


;Thunderbird’s popular junk mail tools have been updated to stay ahead of spam. Each email you receive passes through Thunderbird’s leading-edge junk mail filters. Each time you mark messages as spam, Thunderbird "learns" and improves its filtering so you can spend more time reading the mail that matters. Thunderbird can also use your mail provider’s spam filters to keep junk mail out of your inbox.
Thunderbirds populære spam-filter er blevet forbedret. Hver eneste mail, du modtager, sendes gennem Thunderbirds effektive og innovative spam-filter. Hver gang du markerer en mail som værende spam, lærer Thunderbird og forbedrer sit filter. Dermed slipper du for spam, så du kan koncentrere dig om de mails, der betyder noget. Thunderbird kan også bruge din mailudbyders spam-filtre til at holde spam-mail ude af din indbakke.


;Open Source
Open Source {ok}


;At the heart of Thunderbird is an open source development process driven by thousands of passionate, experienced developers and security experts spread all over the world. Our openness and active community of experts helps to ensure our products are more secure and quickly updated, while also enabling us to take advantage of the best third party security scanning and evaluation tools to further bolster overall security.
Hjertet i Thunderbird er en open source udviklingsproces, der drives af tusinder af passionerede, erfarne udviklere og sikkerhedseksperter, spredt over hele verden. Vores åbenhed og eksperterne i vores aktive community hjælper os med at holde vores produkter sikre og opdaterede. Det gør os samtidig også i stand til at benytte de bedste tredjeparts sikkerhedsværktøjer til skanning og evaluering for yderligere at fasttømre den overordnede sikkerhed.


